"lifeSummary":"William d'Aumarle(이)가 1320년 영국 코른월에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 William D'Aumarle(은)는 25세였고, 그의 어머니 Isabel Meriet(은)는 25세였다. 그는 1342년 영국 데폰 램르턴에서 Agnes Helen de Meriet(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 두 명의 아들과 두 명의 딸을 두었다. 그는 1361년 영국 서머세트 미들일 친옥크에서 41세의 나이로 사망했다."},"lv":{"1320–1361":"1320.gads–1361.gads","1327–1363":"1327–1363","1325–Female":"1325–mirusi","1341–1362":"1341–1362","1342–1399":"1342.gads–1399","1343–1399":"1343.gads–1399","1345–1413":"1345–1413","1296–1335":"1296–1335.gads","1295–1370":"1295–1370","1341":"1341","1363":"1363","1296":"1296","1362":"1362","1361":"1361. gads","1295":"1295","abt 1341":"ap 1341. gadu","1370":"1370","1327":"1327","1337":"1337","1413":"1413","1325":"1325","1335":"1335. gads","1345":"1345","1399":"1399","1343":"1343. gads","1453":"1453","1320":"1320. gads","1342":"1342. gads","about 1315":"ap 1315. gadu","about 1345":"ap 1345. gadu","1328":"1328","Shute, Devon, England":"Shute, Devon, England","Middle Chinnock, Somerset, England":"Middle Chinnock, Somerset, England","England":"England","Lympstone, Devon, England":"Lympstone, Devon, England","Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England","Lamerton, Devon, England":"Lamerton, Devon, England","Woodbury, St. Thomas, Devon, England":"Woodbury with Exton, Devon, England"},"mg":{"1320–1361":"1320–1361","1327–1363":"1327–1363","1325–Female":"1325–Maty","1341–1362":"1341–1362","1342–1399":"1342–1399","1343–1399":"1343–1399","1345–1413":"1345–1413","1296–1335":"1296–1335","1295–1370":"1295–1370","1341":"1341","1363":"1363","1296":"1296","1362":"1362","1361":"1361","1295":"1295","abt 1341":"tany ho any amin'ny 1341","1370":"1370","1327":"1327","1337":"1337","1413":"1413","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1345":"1345","1399":"1399","1343":"1343","1453":"1453","1320":"1320","1342":"1342","about 1315":"tany ho any amin'ny 1315","about 1345":"tany ho any amin'ny 1345","1328":"1328","Shute, Devon, England":"Shute, Devon, England","Middle Chinnock, Somerset, England":"Middle Chinnock, Somerset, England","England":"En